verbose_text: Considering that DNA vaccines are usually based on a single antigen and are largely limited by the major histocompatibility complex (MHC) [XREF_BIBR], pVAX-TgCDPK2 may not readily induce an effective and complete immune response against T. gondii infection.
evidence: pVAX-TgCDPK2 may not readily induce an effective and complete immune response
